        {
            "title": "AI醫療概念落地？ 醫渡科技首次全年盈利",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"280\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/XiusvKC92dx.WmbmB_GbCw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUzOA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/the_bamboo_works_186/29f8a896cc661c5fa1d8c087e9d839f8\" width=\"500\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/ai%E9%86%AB%E7%99%82%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E8%90%BD%E5%9C%B0-%E9%86%AB%E6%B8%A1%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E5%85%A8%E5%B9%B4%E7%9B%88%E5%88%A9-000000015.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-24 08:35:32",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
